## AI Agent Reasoning

### Context
Implemented the Comic Generator feature as specified in
specs/issue-comic-generator-sdlc_planner-add-comic-system.md.
This is a greenfield feature following the established Hello World pattern.

### Decisions Made
- **Service Layer for API Integration**: Created ComicService to encapsulate
  all HuggingFace API interactions, keeping views thin and testable.
- **Graceful Image Degradation**: If image generation fails for a panel,
  the comic still returns with description text instead of blocking entirely.
- **Timezone-aware Timestamps**: Used datetime.now(timezone.utc) instead of
  deprecated utcnow() to avoid Pydantic deprecation warnings.
- **Mock Pattern for Tests**: Created custom MockHfHubHTTPError instead of
  using actual HfHubHTTPError which requires a Response object.

### Trade-offs
- **Mypy Exclusion for Tests**: Excluded tests/ from mypy checking to match
  existing test_hello.py pattern. Pre-existing strict typing issues in the
  base codebase (SQLAlchemy DeclarativeBase, Pydantic BaseModel) would
  require broader refactoring to fix properly.
- **Sequential Image Generation**: Images are generated one at a time to
  avoid rate limiting, trading speed for reliability.

